[Equine herpesvirus type 1 is often associated with abortions as well as
respiratory diseases. Vaccines are available but must be administered
often. - Mod.TG]
[This disease is not on any of the OIE lists of diseases of public health
or socio-economic importance or of concern to international trade. -
Mod.JW]
